# Frontend (embedded static UI)

## Read first

- `internal/web/static/js/api.js` — fetch helpers
- `internal/web/static/js/seats.js`, `payment.js` — page logic
- [docs/design_overview.md](../../docs/design_overview.md) §7

## API contract

- Timer: use `timer_remaining_seconds` from order responses; decrement locally between polls.
- After any mutating call (seats, payment, cancel), refetch `GET /api/v1/flights/{id}/seats?order_id=`.
- Single active order: persist `order_id` in `localStorage`; block new booking until terminal state.
- Highlight own holds via `?order_id=` on seat map GET.
- Optional SSE: `GET /api/v1/orders/{id}/stream`; fallback polling ~2s is acceptable.

